Abstrak: As part of an installation by Mark Jenkins, 84 sculpted figures loom at the edge of rooftops in London. The project is meant to raise awareness of male suicide rates in the United Kingdom, where, on average, 84 men kill themselves every week.
Sumber: Nation. 4/30/2018, Vol. 306 Issue 13, p11-11. 2/3p. 1 Color Photograph
